trans-unit.source: The LdapConnection class creates a TCP/IP or UDP LDAP connection to Microsoft Active Directory Domain Services or an LDAP server.
trans-unit.target: Klassen LdapConnection skapar en TCP/IP- eller UDP LDAP anslutning till Microsoft Active Directory Domain Services eller en LDAP-server.
